 This install applies to "Parasol Stars" © 1992 Ocean, 1 disk.

 This install requires WHDLoad, DIC, RawDIC and The Patcher to be in the path.
 The programs can be found in the WHDLoad package.
 To install from a different drive than DF0: select installation mode Expert.

 The installed program requires 0.5 MB ChipMem and 0.5 MB OtherMem.
 It can be quit by pressing F10 (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, EXPCHIP, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
        http://www.whdload.de/
 or     aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and    aminet:game/patch/

 version 1.5 (15.08.2019) done by JOTD:
 - CUSTOM2=1 enables jump with second/blue button (player 1)
 - CUSTOM2=2 enables jump with second/blue button (player 2).
 - CUSTOM2=3 enables option for both players
 - CUSTOM1=1 enables levelskip
 - CUSTOM1=2 enables cheatmode
 - CUSTOM1=3 enables both (levelskip & cheatmode)
 - added CD32 joypad controls (see below)
 - added quit key for 68000 machines
 - adapted to whdload v17
 - bugfix for version 2 when loading score (address shift error)
 - source code cleanup/rework
 
 version 1.4a (01.09.05) done by CFou!:
 - just new readme

 version 1.4 (17.03.05) done by CFou!:
 - Trainer upgraded
 - Tooltype Custom1=1 used for Levelskip (F1)
   Tooltype Custom1=2 used to activate CheatMode but without game limitations
   (known game limitation in cheat mode-> monsters don't move)

 version 1.3 (13.03.05) done by CFou!:
  - Another version supported
   (Thanks to Denis Lechevalier for ipf's file)
  - Another Rob Northen Copylock protections removed (V2)
  - Manual and Hints files added
  - Tested with Snoop Tootype
  - New install script
  - Some colored icons added
  - Source code included

 version 1.2 done by Dark Angel:
 - removed all cacr accesses, updated for WHDLoad 10+

 version 1.1 done by Dark Angel:
 - Caches are now flushed to work on 060

 version 1.0 to 1.2 done by Dark Angel:
 - initial release
 - Tooltype Custom1=1 used for Levelskip (F1)
   (If you enable the trainer tooltype your scores will not be saved!)
 - Protections removed
 - Highscore saving added (file named 'Highs')
 - Trainer tooltype

Thanks to Wolfgang Unger and Denis Lechevalier for originals.

CD32 controls (player 1 only):

- play: pause
- rev+fwd while paused: give up current game (you have to press several times, sorry about that)
- play+rev+fwd: quit to workbench
- fwd+green: skip level

Notes: the protection is impressive: standard RN copylock but a lot of checksums to see if the protection
has been tampered with. Thumbs up to Dark Angel & CFou! for beating that one. Signed: JOTD

